      "markdown_text": "=====================\n\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\n\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 100, 1280])\n\n=====================\n\n- Archival access: Content dating back to 1997, in most cases, to all titles in your Core Collection.  \n\n- Generous licensing terms: Access journals across multi-site campuses and global corporations, ILL, and walk-in user access for academic institutions.  \n\n- Account Manager and post-sale support: Work with a dedicated Account Manager and take advantage of marketing resources available to promote awareness and usage in your institution. Tailored online training workshops available on request.  \n\n## Changes for 2022  \n\nClick to see journal changes  \n\nJournal Changes Flyer  \n\nDownload Journal Changes Flyer  \n\nJournals on Wiley Online Library  \n\nBrowse Titles  \n\nJournal Price Lists  \n\nView Price Lists  \n\nConnect with Us"
